<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI Service Developer Portfolio | Azure & AI Specialist</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <!-- Google Fonts: Noto Sans KR -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Lucide Icons -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }
        .gradient-bg {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e3a8a 100%);
        }
        .glass-effect {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .project-card:hover .project-image {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        .reveal {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            transition: all 0.8s ease-out;
        }
        .reveal.active {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
        @keyframes pulse-soft {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.7; }
        }
        .animate-pulse-soft {
            animation: pulse-soft 3s infinite;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-900 overflow-x-hidden">

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 transition-all duration-300 py-4 px-6 glass-effect border-b border-white/10 text-white" id="main-nav">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
            <a href="#" class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tighter">AI.ARCHITECT</a>
            <div class="hidden md:flex space-x-10 text-sm font-medium">
                <a href="#hero" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition">홈</a>
                <a href="#about" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition">전문 역량</a>
                <a href="#projects" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition">프로젝트</a>
                <a href="#experience" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition">경력</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition">연락처</a>
            </div>
            <button class="md:hidden" id="mobile-menu-btn">
                <i data-lucide="menu"></i>
            </button>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section id="hero" class="min-h-screen flex items-center pt-20 gradient-bg text-white relative overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Background decorative elements -->
        <div class="absolute top-1/4 -right-20 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-full blur-[100px] animate-pulse-soft"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 -left-20 w-96 h-96 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] animate-pulse-soft"></div>
        
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 relative z-10">
            <div class="space-y-8">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500/20 border border-blue-400/30 text-blue-300 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
                    <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
                        <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-blue-400 opacity-75"></span>
                        <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-blue-500"></span>
                    </span>
                    <span>Azure Cloud & AI Specialist</span>
                </div>
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold leading-tight">
                    클라우드 위에서 <br>
                    <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-cyan-300">지능형 서비스</span>를 <br>
                    설계합니다.
                </h1>
                <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
                    Azure 클라우드 생태계를 기반으로 대규모 B2C 사용자를 위한 실시간 AI 서비스를 구축합니다. 복잡한 데이터를 사용자 가치로 변환하는 'End-to-End' AI 유저 서비스를 지향합니다.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-4">
                    <a href="#projects" class="px-8 py-4 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 rounded-xl font-bold transition flex items-center space-x-2 shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/40">
                        <span>프로젝트 살펴보기</span>
                        <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#contact" class="px-8 py-4 glass-effect hover:bg-white/10 rounded-xl font-bold transition border border-white/20">
                        문의하기
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden lg:flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="relative w-full max-w-md aspect-square">
                    <!-- Placeholder for interactive visual/image -->
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 border-2 border-dashed border-blue-400/30 rounded-full animate-[spin_20s_linear_infinite]"></div>
                    <div class="absolute inset-8 border border-blue-400/20 rounded-full animate-[spin_15s_linear_infinite_reverse]"></div>
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <div class="p-8 glass-effect rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border border-white/10 relative overflow-hidden group">
                            <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-40 h-40 bg-blue-500/20 blur-3xl group-hover:bg-blue-500/40 transition duration-700"></div>
                            <div class="relative z-10 space-y-4">
                                <div class="flex space-x-2">
                                    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-400"></div>
                                    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400"></div>
                                    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-400"></div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="font-mono text-sm text-blue-300">
                                    <p class="mb-1">> Azure.Deploy(AI_Service)</p>
